                  <msItem>
                     <p>HARDINGSTONE and COTES. <persName nymRef="Boudon">
                           <forename>Roger</forename>, son of <persName>master <forename>Roger</forename> de <surname>Boudon</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, 
               the 26 of March, <origDate notBefore="1323-07-08" notAfter="1324-07-07">17 Ed. II</origDate>, grants and assigns in dower, for himself and heirs, to
               <persName nymRef="Boudon">
                           <forename>Isabella</forename>
                        </persName>, his mother,
               formerly wife of the said master Roger, a certain house and the third part of a
               grange, dovecot, 6s. annual rent, together with certain parcels of land in
               <placeName key="place_108016">Hardingstorn</placeName> and <placeName key="place_108009">Cotes</placeName>. 
               Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_108009">Cotes in the parish of Hardingstorn</placeName> the day and year above written. 
               . </p>
